      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior to the pristine interior, making it a rare find for any discerning buyer who demands the very best.",
